Datek Margin Call Mr LARRY CAMPBELL The equity in your Datek Online trading account has fallen below our margin maintenance requirements This results in a margin maintenance call that requires you to either make an immediate payment or to close out some of your portfolio If your account is not restored to its required equity by three business days from today portions of your portfolio may be liquidated Furthermore Datek Online reserves the right to take action at ANY time with or without notice if market conditions warrant Your current margin call is as follows Userid CAMPB When funding your account we strongly recommend that you send any payments by overnight delivery Otherwise your deposit may not be received in time to satisfy this call Please make checks payable to Datek Online and please include your username or account number on the face of your check before mailing to iClearing LLC Attn Margin Dept Wood Avenue South Iselin NJ If we can provide you with further information please contact the Datek Online Customer Support Team at UDatek or or email Thank you Sincerely Margin Department iClearing LLC Member NASDSIPC
